<div class="ultimate-harvester-form">
  <p class="ultimate-harvester-note" style="text-align: center; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;">
    Basic: DC {{tier1DC}} &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    Successful: DC {{tier2DC}} &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    Bountiful: DC {{tier3DC}} &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    Nat 19+: Rare
  </p>

  <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin: 0.3rem 0;">
    <span style="font-size: 0.85rem;">Time spent foraging:</span>
    <button type="button" class="ultimate-harvester-spinner-btn" data-dir="-1" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-minus"></i></button>
    <input type="number" name="hours" value="2" min="0" max="6" step="1" readonly style="width: 2.5rem; text-align: center;" />
    <button type="button" class="ultimate-harvester-spinner-btn" data-dir="1" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
    <span style="font-size: 0.85rem;">hours</span>
  </div>

  <details class="ultimate-harvester-info">
    <summary><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> How does foraging work?</summary>
    <div class="ultimate-harvester-info-content">
      <ul>
        <li>Roll your skill check &mdash; the highest tier you meet determines the quality of your finds</li>
        <li>Better rolls improve both the variety and quantity of what you discover</li>
        <li>Higher tiers have a chance to yield crafting components, alchemical reagents, and rare materials</li>
        <li>Every 2 hours after the first reduces the DC by 1</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="ultimate-harvester-note"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle ultimate-harvester-icon--warning"></i> <strong>Extreme failures</strong> may trigger dangerous events &mdash; all characters involved in the foraging attempt will suffer any negative effects.</p>
    </div>
  </details>
</div>
